Standard React Project .gitignore

Prevents committing dependencies, build files, and temporary artifacts.

Dependency Folders

Node.js dependencies

/node_modules

Yarn 2/3 dependencies

.yarn/cache
.pnp.*

Build Artifacts

Production build folder (might be 'dist' or 'build')

/build
/dist
/out
/public/build

Temporary Files

Logs

.log
npm-debug.log
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.npm

IDE and Editor Folders/Files

Visual Studio Code

.vscode/

IntelliJ/Webstorm

.idea/

Environment and Config Files

Environment variables (Crucial: never commit secrets or API keys)

.env
.env.development
.env.production
.env.local

Local config file

config.local.json

Operating System Files

.DS_Store # macOS
Thumbs.db # Windows